trans-unit.target: TEXT_REGLAKMASTERCRAFTER_00160_TALAN_000_000<tab>Don't know you, don't care to. Git, 'fore I blast ye in the arse with rock salt!
TEXT_REGLAKMASTERCRAFTER_00160_TALAN_000_010<tab>Hm, Guiding Star thinks yer goody-nuff? You're ready for some gatherin', I hope, or we all three goin' to be sorry...
